mapLocationData.name: Mokutan Village
mapLocationData.description: A village that earns its revenue by producing coal for the lords of the region, called Diamyo. This village's economy boomed as it was ideally placed in the middle of a great forest and capable of sourcing the wood for the charcoal production.

missionData.name: Searching for the Past
missionData.description: The only thing you can think to do is look for answers in the nearby village you've been informed of.

dialogLines.dialogText: You walk onto the main street. You begin to notice people along the street glaring at you as you make your way.
A humongous cart barely misses you as it rolls swiftly past and kicks up large chunks of mud as it does.
"Fool!?" You curse at the driver in surprise; flinching from the cold sensation of the mud absorbing into your cloths.
Brushing off the mess you realize that your cloths and skin were already filthy to begin with.
You look around to see if anyone had witnessed this rude exchange. No one seems to care.
Then you notice two armored guards down the way. They brandish clubs as they mumble to one another and begin walking toward you.
Without warning someone runs by and grabs your arm. Yanking you down an alleyway.
You run with this cloaked person, their slight frame gliding over the uneven dirt street.
As you both round the corner they let go of your arm and lurch to a holt. They face you and pull down their hood.
"You've gotta be more careful around here. The new industry in this town has attracted all sorts of undesirable folks" blerts out this dingy young person as they scratch their head impulsively.
"Right...yeah." Glancing back around the corner. It seems there isn't anyone pursuing you two.
"You seem lost. I can help you find what you seek...for a price." They flash a big smile, revealing several missing teeth.
"Oh... " you mutter as you look down at your person, considering what items you're willing to part with. As you begin inspecting your inventory your stomach growls audibly.
They grimace in reaction. "Wow. You really fell on hard times, didn't you?"
Your face becomes solumn as you nod your reply.
They take a deep breath and sign. "Alright, how about we find something to eat first and get back to business later."

dialographyData_Pre.locationDescSummary: This person who seemingly helped you avoid a confrontation is now asking for payment in exchange for information. They suggest that they'll stick around until they get their payday.

dialogLines.dialogText: This is the village you heard about.
It's many streets and bustling crowds stretch out before you. Standing motionless on the outskirts, the commotion heightening your anxiety.
